"collections <sharding>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/faq/developers.txt:622
msgid ""
"You **cannot** use :method:`~cursor.snapshot()` with "
":method:`~cursor.sort()` or :method:`~cursor.hint()` cursor methods."
